&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;flood the nimbus log. (2.0.1.y is our internal version. The code is basically community 2.0.0)&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This is similar to the issue found in Thrift community and got fixed in 0.13.0 but it&apos;s not released yet &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/THRIFT-4805&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/THRIFT-4805&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
